window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Lance was living a rather boring life as an office worker. That is, until he suffered a fiery death. </b></p> <p>Now he's been reborn as a combat mage, a versatile spellcaster from a dying sect of mighty warriors. With his new dragonblood abilities and the help of a brash augmenter, a beautiful arcane weaver and a deadly swordswoman, Lance will have to survive the land of Oracle, a world where power is manifested from the blood of gods...that, or die trying.</p> <p><i>This novel contains progression, harem, and LitRPG elements. It is intended for mature audiences. </i></p>"; 
